content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4215.26 - Payments to the New York State Quarter Horse Breeding and Development Fund

State Regulations

Every corporation or association shall pay to the New

York State Quarter Horse Breeding and Development Fund the percentage of the
pari-mutuel pool as required by law when the payments of State taxes are due to
the State Tax Commission. Notes
